00:26.735 --> 00:28.112
a journalist,

00:28.278 --> 00:29.905
safari guide,

00:30.072 --> 00:31.665
foreign intelligence agent,

00:31.823 --> 00:34.246
and a veterinary pathologist.

00:34.409 --> 00:37.458
Our task: to Hnd out what is
happening with the animals,

00:37.621 --> 00:41.797
